## Delta Compression

### Full State vs Delta

| Approach | Bandwidth | Use When |
|----------|-----------|----------|
| Full state | High | Initial sync, resync |
| Delta | Low | Steady state updates |
| Keyframe + delta | Medium | Periodic full, delta between |

### Delta Encoding

Send only changed fields since last acknowledged state.

```cpp
struct StateDelta {
    uint32_t from_tick;
    uint32_t to_tick;
    std::vector<EntityDelta> changes;
};

struct EntityDelta {
    EntityId id;
    std::vector<FieldChange> fields;  // Only changed
};
```

### Delta Rules

- [ ] Delta from last confirmed state
- [ ] Include tick numbers for ordering
- [ ] Full state sent periodically (keyframe) to recover from loss
- [ ] Delta size bounded; fall back to full if delta larger

